{"tid":2412225,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"正視聽:美國都有科技公司幫政府監控人民","createTime":"2021-02-18T01:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T08:49:31.000Z","uid":113951,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"20cd788c9fb74125f978c0c849ef53ff0aa2deaf","tid":2412225,"uid":113951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T01:57:59.000Z","msg":"五毛收皮啦<br />\n人地真係用黎反恐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//Palantir是一間「大數據」公司，有幾個你一定聽過的美國大客戶：CIA, NSA, FBI和DHS(國土安全部) - 還好還暫時沒有CCP。也有細摩(JPMorgan)等一些金融機構的反詐騙、反洗黑錢和風險管理部門。 有留意美股的讀者，也可能對此公司略有所聞。 <br />\n<br />\n 這些機構的共通點，就是為了捉到目標人物(恐怖份子、罪犯、黑客、間諜、內鬼、或者是異見人士)，都需要從大量的數據中，看出其中不同資料之間的複雜關聯，快速地做出準確的情報分析。<br />\n<br />\nPalantir的產品中，有兩條主要的Product line：Gotham和Foundry(前身為Metropolis)。產品Gotham(就是取自蝙蝠俠中的葛咸城)最重要Value proposition，就是可以在海量資料中找到極少數的「壞人」(Bad actor)。<br />\n<br />\n  而美國在2001後的近十年，最重要的「壞人」，相信只有&mdash;個 - 奧薩瑪&middot;賓&middot;拉登。//<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/602db508da97cc6a75de03f8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fblackmirrortech%2Fshow%2F602db508da97cc6a75de03f8&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOnIsb0SIwbGp5IKHDv9YBGc%3D&h=5442ede4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/blackmirrortech/show/602db508da97cc6a75de03f8</a>"},{"pid":"0cfecc66096177e01fc38423dfa100e6ff52ab5a","tid":2412225,"uid":18948,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T02:00:58.000Z","msg":"PLTR 哭喪區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2307219\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2307219</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f1337f93b63a064723adee5e6be43928438eab46","tid":2412225,"uid":113951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0cfecc66096177e01fc38423dfa100e6ff52ab5a","tid":2412225,"uid":18948,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T02:00:58.000Z","msg":"PLTR 哭喪區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2307219\" data-auto-link target=\"